ters.com/business/autos-transportation/chery-launches-28000-euro-crossover-suv-italy-it-plans-europe-expansion-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国奇瑞汽车正在评估其在欧洲扩大生产能力和销售的选择，其汽油版 Omoda 5 跨界 SUV 开始在意大利销售，售价为 27,900 欧元（30,182 美元）起。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:27:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chery-launches-28000-euro-crossover-suv-italy-it-plans-europe-expansion-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行可动用数千亿元债券为多头涨势降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-has-hundreds-billions-yuan-bonds-its-disposal-cool-long-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国央行周五对路透表示，中国央行拥有价值数千亿元人民币的债券可供借用，并将根据市场情况出售这些债券，市场认为该计划的一部分是为了给强劲的债券涨势降温。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 06:32:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-has-hundreds-billions-yuan-bonds-its-disposal-cool-long-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国上汽集团寻求欧盟委员会就电动汽车关税举行听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-motor-seeks-european-commission-hearings-ev-tariffs-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国上汽集团周五表示，随着欧盟对中国制造电动汽车的临时关税生效，该公司将要求欧盟委员会就其面临的额外关税举行听证会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 06:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-motor-seeks-european-commission-hearings-ev-tariffs-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国正在努力利用储能的繁荣，呼吁更多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-struggling-make-use-boom-energy-storage-calls-even-more-2024-07-05/</link><description>在中国山东省的一片贫瘠的土地上，一排排看起来像薄薄的白色集装箱的东西排列在一起。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 05:42:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-struggling-make-use-boom-energy-storage-calls-even-more-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商如何在储能领域脱颖而出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-chinas-ev-battery-makers-stack-up-energy-storage-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国电动汽车电池巨头CATL 300750.SZ和BYD 002594.SZ正在关注不断增长的固定储能市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 05:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-chinas-ev-battery-makers-stack-up-energy-storage-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院听取黄之锋和其他民主党人的减刑请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-hears-mitigation-pleas-joshua-wong-other-democrats-2024-07-05/</link><description>著名香港活动家黄之锋的律师周五表示，黄之锋应被视为涉及 47 名民主党人的具有里程碑意义的颠覆案件的积极参与者，但他敦促法院因他提前认罪而从轻判刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-hears-mitigation-pleas-joshua-wong-other-democrats-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>香港零售商指望提高免税配额以促进销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-retailers-bank-duty-free-quota-hike-boost-sales-2024-07-05/</link><description>增加中国游客赴港免税配额可能会在一定程度上支持该市的零售商，但来自内地的游客表示，价格仍然没有吸引力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:58:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-retailers-bank-duty-free-quota-hike-boost-sales-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大为批准关键矿产的大型并购交易设定了很高的标准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/canada-sets-high-bar-approving-large-ma-deals-critical-minerals-2024-07-05/</link><description>加拿大周四向采矿业发出通知，任何针对该国关键矿产生产商的重大交易只有在“最特殊的情况下”才会获得批准。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/canada-sets-high-bar-approving-large-ma-deals-critical-minerals-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告中国更多军事活动，呼吁缓和局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-more-chinese-military-activity-calls-de-escalation-2024-07-05/</link><description>台湾周五报道称，中国在附近重新进行了军事活动，并进行了另一次“战斗巡逻”，政府呼吁北京在扣押一艘台湾渔船后不要加剧紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:45:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-more-chinese-military-activity-calls-de-escalation-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车关税生效，中国公布了欧盟白兰地调查的下一步措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-take-talks-seriously-ev-tariffs-go-into-effect-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国周五宣布对欧洲白兰地进口进行反倾销调查的下一步，在欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车临时关税生效的同一天，紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-take-talks-seriously-ev-tariffs-go-into-effect-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>世界股市创历史新高，英国工党压倒性胜利和美国就业人数成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-05/</link><description>周五晚些时候，在关键就业数据公布之前，对美国降息的乐观情绪支撑了市场情绪，世界股市创下新高，而本周末法国大选之前，欧元触及三周高点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:18:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>美元在非农就业数据公布前大幅下跌；英镑大获全胜英国大选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-three-week-lows-pound-takes-uk-election-stride-2024-07-05/</link><description>周五，在可能影响利率前景的非农就业数据公布之前，美元处于近三周低点附近的守势，而英镑则坚挺，因为工党有望在英国大选中赢得绝大多数席位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:08:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-three-week-lows-pound-takes-uk-election-stride-2024-07-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>